    <string name="service_label">PureShield</string>
    <string name="service_description">PureShield uses Accessibility Service only to detect supported distraction screens (like Shorts, Reels, and TikTok) and block them locally on your device.\n\nIt reads the active window content inside the apps you choose so it can identify those screens, and it does not send that information off your device.</string>
